    <section class="design-system-section panel-inverse panel--wide">
        <div class="grid-width">
            <h3 class="design-system-headline" id="forms">Groupings in our forms</h3>
            <p>Our forms are made up of three types of groupings which form the hierarchy of how we display information to our users:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Form fragments (question groupings)</li>
                <li>Questions</li>
                <li>Question options</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This hierarchy improves usability by allowing people to see at a glance what information will be needed to complete the form whilst still getting the detail they need to answer each question.</p>
        </div>
